<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body{
            font-family: -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,"Helvetica Neue",Arial,sans-serif,"Apple Color Emoji","Segoe UI Emoji","Segoe UI Symbol";
        }
        h5{
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-family: inherit;
            font-weight: 500;
            line-height: 1.2;
            color: black;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        p{
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: block;
            margin-block-start: 1em;
            margin-block-end: 1em;
            margin-inline-start: 0px;
            margin-inline-end: 0px;
        }
        .card{
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.125);
            border-radius: .25rem;
            width: 50%;
        }
        .btn{
            display: inline-block;
            font-weight: 400;
            text-align: center;
            white-space: nowrap;
            vertical-align: middle;
            user-select: none;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
            padding: .375rem .75rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
            border-radius: .25rem;
            transition: all .15s ease-in-out;
            color: white !important;
            background-color: #007bff;
            border-color: #007bff;
        }
        .btn:not(:disabled):not(.disabled) {
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .card-body {
            -webkit-box-flex: 1;
            flex: 1 1 auto;
            padding: 1.25rem;
        }
        a{
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        img{
            width: 100%;
            display: block;
            vertical-align: middle;
            border-style: none;
        }
        .card-header{
            padding: .75rem 1.25rem;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            background-color: rgba(0,0,0,.03);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.125);
        }
    </style>
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
            <img src="https://i.ibb.co/Y8TrkTs/Untitled.png" alt="logo">
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <h5>Cinepolis Web</h5>
            <p>Bienvenido, este email llega debido a que te registraste a nuestro portal web.
                <br>Tu nueva contrase√±a: {{pass}}
                <br>Si no reconoces este email, porfavor ignorarlo.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>